This Project has the target to create a compleatly open source Brushless Drive Controller.

The controller uses an AT90PWM3 controller from Atmel.

The Application notes used for designing the circuits can be found here:
http://www.atmel.com/dyn/resources/prod_documents/doc7518.pdf
http://www.atmel.com/dyn/resources/prod_documents/doc7658.pdf

Cheers Piotr Esden-Tempski
